org.mobicents.slee.container
Class SleeContainer

java.lang.Object
  org.mobicents.slee.container.SleeContainer

public class SleeContainer
extends java.lang.Object

Implements the SleeContainer. The SleeContainer is the anchor for the SLEE. It is the central location from where all container modules are accessible.

Author:
F.Moggia, M. Ranganathan, Ivelin Ivanov, Emil Ivov, Tim Fox, eduardomartins
